WEBVTT

00:05:29.777 --> 00:05:34.676
Shared memories --
that's where the old BBC building was;

00:05:34.676 --> 00:05:39.601
and personal memories --
that's where I gave my first kiss.

00:05:39.601 --> 00:05:44.034
They also recalled how some paths
smelled and sounded.

00:05:44.034 --> 00:05:47.261
So what if we had a mapping tool

00:05:47.261 --> 00:05:49.792
that would return
the most enjoyable routes

00:05:49.792 --> 00:05:52.412
based not only on aesthetics

00:05:52.412 --> 00:05:55.721
but also based on smell, sound, 
and memories?

00:05:55.721 --> 00:05:59.826
That's where our research
is going right now.

00:05:59.826 --> 00:06:02.028
More generally, my research,